{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/little-smile-sebuah-komik-tentang-dilema-keluarga-jaman-sekarang/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Little Smile: Sebuah Komik Tentang Dilema Keluarga Jaman Sekarang","content":"<p>Bro sis ada yang uda pernah baca manga bahasa Indonesia berjudul “Little Smile” ? Komik <em>one shot</em> menyentuh hati ini sempat viral di media sosial loh! Kalau bro sis belum tahu, kita kasih sedikit <em>review </em>komik drama ini nih. Jadi komik Little Smile<em> </em>ini bercerita tentang seorang bapak tukang becak yang berasal dari kota Yogyakarta. Bapak ini sangat gigih mencari kerja, mengayuh becak sepanjang waktu dan selalu tersenyum. Senyuman itu seolah-olah menunjukan betapa semangatnya beliau untuk mewujudkan sebuah mimpinya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4816\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4816\" data-attachment-id=\"4816\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-dragon-ball-yang-terbaru-membawa-son-goku-ke-level-berikutnya/attachment/1-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-4816 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4816\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Komik Little Smile bersetting di kota Yogyakarta. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4825\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4825\" data-attachment-id=\"4825\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-dragon-ball-yang-terbaru-membawa-son-goku-ke-level-berikutnya/attachment/4-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-4825 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4825\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Potongan scene komik Little Smile. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4822\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4822\" data-attachment-id=\"4822\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-dragon-ball-yang-terbaru-membawa-son-goku-ke-level-berikutnya/attachment/3-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"3\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-4822 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4822\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Scene komik Little Smile. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p>Cerita ini menimbulkan berbagai macam reaksi dari yang membacanya. Ada yang tersentuh, mengerenyutkan dahi dan bahkan termotivasi untuk lebih gigih dan ikhlas dalam bekerja.</p>\n<p>Kisah ayah dan anak memang sedang banyak menjadi sorotan akhir-akhir ini. Hal ini terjadi mungkin karena ayah dan anak memiliki hubungan yang cukup emosional. Terbukti dari kesuksesan film <em>LOGAN</em> dan<em> Guardian of The Galaxy</em> yang notabenene mengangkat kisah hubungan antara ayah dan anak.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4819\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4819\" data-attachment-id=\"4819\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-dragon-ball-yang-terbaru-membawa-son-goku-ke-level-berikutnya/attachment/2-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-4819 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4819\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Potongan scene komik Little Smile. (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p>Thoma Prayoga sang <em>author</em>, sejauh ini sudah menerbitkan dua judul komik <em>one shot</em> di <a href=\"http://www.ciayo.com\">CIAYO Comics</a>. Komik Indonesia buatannya kebanyakan bernuansa keluarga dengan tone hangat yang mampu menarik atensi dari pembacanya. Sebuah tema komik online yang genrenya masih tidak berbanding jauh dengan komik “Payung”, hanya bedanya pada komik Payung, Thoma sama sekali tidak memberikan balon dialog sama sekali.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_2571\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2571\" data-attachment-id=\"2571\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/payung-komik-viral-yang-bikin-mewek/attachment/body3-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Komik Payung (ciayo.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Komik Payung (ciayo.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2571\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3.jpg\" alt=\"Komik Payung (ciayo.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-2571\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Komik Payung (ciayo.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di bulan puasa, kayaknya asik juga kalo para pecinta komik ngabuburit sambil baca komik Indonesia di CIAYO Comics, salah satunya Little Smile. Diharapkan komik ini bisa memotivasi kamu untuk bersikap lebih baik dan menghargai kerja keras kedua orang tuamu. Bro sis yang uda ga sabar baca komik Little Smile ini, bro sis bisa langsung klik <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/comic/little-smile/detail\">disini</a>. Oya, kalo penasaran dengan komik Payung, CIAYO Blog juga pernah ngebahas detail mengenai komiknya loh, kalian bisa baca artikelnya <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/payung-komik-viral-yang-bikin-mewek/\">disini</a>.</p>\n<p>Bro sis ada yang suka buat komik <em>one shot</em>? Ato tertarik dan tertantang buat cerita <em>one shot</em> setelah membaca artikel ini? Nah, setelah sukses dengan One Shot Challenge Vol.1 dan tingginya antusiame masyarakat akan lomba ini, CIAYO Comics kembali mengadakan <strong><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ciayo-one-shot-challenge-vol-2/\">CIAYO Comics One Shot Challenge Vol. 2</a></strong> loh! untuk info mengenai <em>challenge</em>, bro sis bisa klik <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ciayo-one-shot-challenge-vol-2/\">disini</a>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_3824\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3824\" data-attachment-id=\"3824\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/indonesia-harus-mulai-melirik-intellectual-property-sebagai-komoditi-industri/attachment/body2-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Poster CIAYO Comics One-shot Challenge Vol. 2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster CIAYO Comics One-shot Challenge Vol. 2 (CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-15-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3824\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-15.jpg\" alt=\"Poster CIAYO Comics One-shot Challenge Vol. 2 (CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-15.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/body2-15-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-3824\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster CIAYO Comics One-shot Challenge Vol. 2 (CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"f3c6bf29-0a0e-513c-9b4f-f4294c9b5f0b"}}}